        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-18T14:19:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think that is more clear, but I omitted the embedding. I\u0027m not a huge fan and that would result in a pretty invasive change at the moment.",
      "parentUuid": "60fc41e7_3e7f02c5",
      "range": {
